text.section:
The board shall consist of the:
Secretary of the Finance and Administration Cabinet;
Secretary of the Personnel Cabinet;
Secretary of the Labor Cabinet; and
Seven (7) at-large members appointed by the Governor, subject to confirmation by the Senate.

No person shall serve on the board who:
Fails to meet or comply with the conflict of interest policies established by the board and KRS 304.24-270;
Is not bondable;
Is an employee, attorney, or contractor of a competing insurer providing workers' compensation insurance in the Commonwealth; or
Is not a resident of this Commonwealth.
